# LucidGate example list: bannedmimetypelist
# Format: One MIME type per line. Use lowercase type/subtype where possible.
# Lines beginning with # are comments and are ignored by the loader.
# To activate a rule, copy one example, remove the leading # and adapt it to your environment.
# You can include another file with: .Include<relative-or-absolute-path>
#
# Commented examples:
# application/x-msdownload
# application/x-dosexec
# application/x-sh
# application/java-archive
# application/vnd.android.package-archive
# application/octet-stream
# application/x-msi
# application/x-mach-binary
# application/x-elf
# application/x-executable
